{"data": [{"id": "4741588", "title": "'Drill, Baby, Drill!'", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://media.gettyimages.com/id/465352723/photo/driller-in-a-quarry.jpg?b=1&amp;s=612x612&amp;w=0&amp;k=20&amp;c=LuE5_rPPtskMMxL1aOKgmIJVmr9KwsYRSSC6RfkSA0g=\" alt=\"driller in a quarry\" data-id=\"465352723\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">hsvrs/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong><em>Editor's Note:</em></strong> <em>Originally published at <a href=\"https://tsi-blog.com/2024/12/drill-baby-drill/\" rel=\"nofollow\">tsi-blog.com</a> on N</em><em>ovember 20, 2024</em></p> <p><em>[This blog post is an excerpt from a commentary published last week at <a href=\"https://speculative-investor.com/\" rel=\"noopener\">www.speculative-investor.com</a>]</em></p> <p>The phrase \u201cDrill baby drill\u201d has been around for a long time, but Trump</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741588-drill-baby-drill", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 23:41:00"}, {"id": "4741586", "title": "BlackRock's Growth Could Be Reaching A Ceiling", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178095442/image_2178095442.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Brooklyn Bridge Aerial\" data-id=\"2178095442\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178095442/image_2178095442.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178095442/image_2178095442.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178095442/image_2178095442.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178095442/image_2178095442.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178095442/image_2178095442.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178095442/image_2178095442.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178095442/image_2178095442.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178095442/image_2178095442.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Art Wager/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>BlackRock's (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BLK\" title=\"BlackRock, Inc.\">BLK</a></span>) growth to $11.5 trillion in assets under management puts the company at the front of the line for problems in the next financial crisis.</p> <h2>BlackRock's stunning growth has headwinds</h2> <p>BlackRock announced in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178095442/image_2178095442.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741586-blackrocks-growth-could-be-reaching-a-ceiling", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 23:30:46"}, {"id": "4741566", "title": "Ibotta: A Story Worth Keeping An Eye On", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1440510182/image_1440510182.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Cutting Out Coupons\" data-id=\"1440510182\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1440510182/image_1440510182.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1440510182/image_1440510182.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1440510182/image_1440510182.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1440510182/image_1440510182.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1440510182/image_1440510182.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1440510182/image_1440510182.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1440510182/image_1440510182.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1440510182/image_1440510182.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">SolStock/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Today we take a deeper look at coupon platform operator <strong>Ibotta, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IBTA\" title=\"Ibotta, Inc.\">IBTA</a></span>)</strong> which has recently announced a $100 million share buyback. The company\u2019s growth is decelerating after landing <strong>Walmart (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/WMT\" title=\"Walmart Inc.\">WMT</a>)</strong> as a \u2018publisher\u2019 to host</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1440510182/image_1440510182.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741566-ibotta-a-story-worth-keeping-an-eye-on", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 23:25:16"}, {"id": "4741575", "title": "An Update On NUGT: The Leveraged Senior Gold Mining ETF", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145158250/image_145158250.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Gold ingots and coins close up\" data-id=\"145158250\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5224px\" height=\"4016px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145158250/image_145158250.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145158250/image_145158250.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145158250/image_145158250.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145158250/image_145158250.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145158250/image_145158250.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145158250/image_145158250.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145158250/image_145158250.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145158250/image_145158250.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Anthony Bradshaw</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I last wrote about the <b>Direxion Daily Gold Miners Index Bull 2X Shares ETF</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NUGT\" title=\"Direxion Daily Gold Miners Index Bull 2X Shares ETF\">NUGT</a></span>) on <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4653728-nugt-disappointment-weighs-on-the-leveraged-junior-gold-mining-etf\">Seeking Alpha</a> on November 22, 2023, just over one year ago. In that article, I concluded:</p> <blockquote><p><em>I favor a dynamic approach</em></p></blockquote>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145158250/image_145158250.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741575-an-update-on-nugt-the-leveraged-senior-gold-mining-etf", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 23:14:14"}, {"id": "4741570", "title": "Agree Realty: 3 Reasons To Sell And Buy Realty Income", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173613768/image_173613768.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='cat: don\"t look back in anger' data-id=\"173613768\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173613768/image_173613768.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173613768/image_173613768.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173613768/image_173613768.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173613768/image_173613768.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173613768/image_173613768.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173613768/image_173613768.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173613768/image_173613768.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173613768/image_173613768.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\">Our Cat Does Not Like The Valuation On Agree Realty</p> <p class=\"item-credits\">izold/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Our <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/trapping-value/analysis?ticker=ADC\">previous takes</a> on <b>Agree Realty Corporation</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ADC\" title=\"Agree Realty Corporation\">ADC</a></span>) have been on the neutral side, and we have only come away with a \u201chold\u201d rating. The stock</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173613768/image_173613768.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741570-agree-realty-3-reasons-to-sell-and-buy-realty-income", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 23:03:25"}, {"id": "4741568", "title": "Joby Aviation: How The Toyota Partnership Brings More Than Just Funding", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399906856/image_1399906856.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Future mode of transport with electric and unmanned vehicles\" data-id=\"1399906856\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399906856/image_1399906856.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399906856/image_1399906856.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399906856/image_1399906856.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399906856/image_1399906856.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399906856/image_1399906856.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399906856/image_1399906856.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399906856/image_1399906856.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399906856/image_1399906856.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">mikkelwilliam</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Joby Aviation's stock (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/JOBY\" title=\"Joby Aviation, Inc.\">JOBY</a></span>) is still on the rise amid the current investor excitement in the eVTOL space, despite some uncertainties around the exact timeline for its FAA type rating approval.</p> <p></p> <p>Since the release of <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/filing/9216762\">Q3 earnings results</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399906856/image_1399906856.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741568-joby-aviation-toyota-partnership-brings-more-than-just-funding", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 23:00:14"}, {"id": "4741564", "title": "New Import Tariffs Will Be Bad For Ford But I Remain Bullish", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392303787/image_1392303787.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Dealership of the multinational automobile company Ford\" data-id=\"1392303787\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1141px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392303787/image_1392303787.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392303787/image_1392303787.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392303787/image_1392303787.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392303787/image_1392303787.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392303787/image_1392303787.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392303787/image_1392303787.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392303787/image_1392303787.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392303787/image_1392303787.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Neme Jimenez/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>There is no shortage of challenges facing Ford Motor Company (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/F\" title=\"Ford Motor Company\">F</a></span>). Whenever things started to look promising in the last three years, Ford faced a new challenge. Donald Trump's thumping victory in the 2024 Presidential election seems to have unlocked a</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392303787/image_1392303787.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741564-new-import-tariffs-will-be-bad-for-ford-but-i-remain-bullish", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 22:45:42"}, {"id": "4741563", "title": "GameStop: Is This Time Different?", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"GameStop store sign\" data-id=\"1303187579\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3975px\" height=\"2650px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/g